		 <h1>Adam Jermyn</h1>

            <h2>About Me</h2>

            <p>
		I'm a physicist with interests in out-of-equilibrium phenomena and statistical physics. My recent projects have largely been
		in astrophysics, but I also work on tensor networks, biological self-assembly, and quantum transport processes.
            </p>

